text: Vanessa Lee Carlton (born August 16, 1980) is an American singer. She was born in Milford, Pennsylvania. In 2002 her first album Be Not Nobody was released. It reached number one in Australia. ==Personal life== Carlton came out as bisexual on June 19, 2010. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:LGBT people from Pennsylvania Category:American pianists Category:American pop musicians Category:American rock singers Category:American singer-songwriters Category:Bisexual people Category:LGBT musicians Category:Living people Category:Singers from Pennsylvania
